document_data.name: Seskaya Atnall
document_data.mainbody: '''Seskaya Atnall''' was an innkeeper in [[Mulmaster]] in [[1373 DR]].
document_data.History: Seskaya was born in [[Zhentil Keep]] where her parents were [[Zhentarim]] spies. When she was a teenager, all the family was relocated to Mulmaster under the orders of their [[Zhent]] masters. When her parents went on a mission out of Mulmaster and never returned, Seskaya continued to work for the Zhentarim.
document_data.Activities: Seskaya managed the [[Sleeping Serpent]] inn, a Zhent safe house in Mulmaster. She was always surrounded by suitors, whom Seskaya used only as a source of information to give to the Zhents.
